Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的臉上黏著什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.89,0:03:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.09,0:04:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是你的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑠川同學泡的紅茶果然很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小爸爸就在這方面教了我很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶葉也是爸爸特地從英國帶回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是正統啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都能喝到這麼好喝的紅茶  太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:33.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也很香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上為兩位準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank  you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我們馬上開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圍繞永不凋零的櫻花發生過的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:03.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天去向老師們打聽一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向老師們打聽？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.77,0:06:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻花上一次凋零是20多年前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該有很多老師知道些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實有可能找到一些線索呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就去圖書室調查一下過去的文獻好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊  那明天就要分頭行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.72,0:06:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸  歌丸  歌丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  不要亂動
